statements: SELECT * FROM RealEstateTokenizationPlatform;
SELECT property_name, property_value FROM RealEstateTokenizationPlatform WHERE property_address = '1234 Main St';
SELECT property_id, property_address, ownership_percentage FROM RealEstateTokenizationPlatform WHERE property_value > 500000 ORDER BY property_value DESC;
SELECT * FROM RealEstateTokenizationPlatform WHERE owner_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426655440000';
SELECT property_name, owner_id FROM RealEstateTokenizationPlatform WHERE ownership_percentage >= 20 ORDER BY property_name ASC;
SELECT property_id, property_name, property_address FROM RealEstateTokenizationPlatform WHERE property_value > 100000 ORDER BY property_value DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM RealEstateTokenizationPlatform WHERE ownership_percentage >= 0.5 ORDER BY property_name ASC LIMIT 10;
SELECT property_name AS Name, property_address AS Address, property_value AS Value FROM RealEstateTokenizationPlatform WHERE owner_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000';
SELECT AVG(property_value) AS average_value, SUM(ownership_percentage) AS total_ownership FROM RealEstateTokenizationPlatform GROUP BY owner_id;
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_properties, MAX(property_value) AS max_value FROM RealEstateTokenizationPlatform WHERE ownership_percentage < 0.2;
SELECT * FROM property WHERE value > 10000
SELECT address, value FROM property ORDER BY address ASC
SELECT * FROM property WHERE owner_id = 3
SELECT address, value FROM property WHERE owner_id = 2 ORDER BY value DESC
SELECT p.address, o.name FROM property p JOIN owner o ON p.owner_id = o.owner_id
SELECT * FROM property WHERE value > 10000 AND owner_id = 1 ORDER BY address DESC;
SELECT property_id, address, value, name FROM property INNER JOIN owner ON property.owner_id = owner.owner_id WHERE name LIKE 'J%' ORDER BY value ASC;
SELECT address, value FROM property WHERE owner_id IN (SELECT owner_id FROM owner WHERE email LIKE '%@gmail.com');
SELECT MAX(value) AS highest_value FROM property;
SELECT * FROM property WHERE owner_id = 2 AND value BETWEEN 5000 AND 10000 ORDER BY property_id ASC;
SELECT * FROM property ORDER BY city ASC;
SELECT address, city, token_price FROM property WHERE token_price > 500000;
SELECT * FROM owner WHERE phone_number LIKE '%123%';
SELECT id, property_id, owner_id, token_price FROM tokenization WHERE token_price BETWEEN 1000 AND 5000;
SELECT id, full_name FROM owner ORDER BY full_name DESC;
SELECT * FROM property WHERE city = 'New York' ORDER BY zipcode DESC;
SELECT id, address, token_price FROM property WHERE token_price > 100000 ORDER BY token_price ASC;
SELECT full_name, email FROM owner WHERE phone_number LIKE '%123%';
SELECT p.address, o.full_name, t.token_count FROM property p JOIN owner o ON p.id = o.id JOIN tokenization t ON p.id = t.property_id WHERE t.token_count > 10 ORDER BY t.token_count DESC;
SELECT DISTINCT city FROM property WHERE zipcode LIKE '1%' ORDER BY city ASC;
SELECT * FROM Properties;
SELECT property_name, property_value FROM Properties;
SELECT owner_name, email, phone_number FROM Owners;
SELECT transaction_date, transaction_type FROM Transactions;
SELECT property_id, owner_id, share_percentage FROM OwnershipShares;
SELECT * FROM Properties WHERE property_value > 100000
SELECT property_name, property_address FROM Properties ORDER BY property_name DESC

SELECT Properties.property_name, Owners.owner_name, OwnershipShares.share_percentage FROM Properties JOIN OwnershipShares ON Properties.id = OwnershipShares.property_id JOIN Owners ON OwnershipShares.owner_id = Owners.id
SELECT Transactions.transaction_type, COUNT(*) FROM Transactions GROUP BY Transactions.transaction_type HAVING COUNT(*) > 1
SELECT Owners.owner_name, Transactions.transaction_date FROM Owners JOIN Transactions ON Owners.id = Transactions.owner_id ORDER BY Transactions.transaction_date ASC
SELECT * FROM property;
SELECT id, name, city FROM owner WHERE id = 1;
SELECT address, city, state FROM property WHERE city = 'New York';
SELECT * FROM token ORDER BY price DESC;
SELECT name, email, phone FROM owner WHERE name LIKE '%John%';
SELECT * FROM property WHERE state = 'California';
SELECT name, address, city FROM property WHERE city = 'New York' ORDER BY name DESC;

SELECT owner.name, token.token_name, transaction.timestamp FROM owner INNER JOIN token ON owner.id = token.owner_id INNER JOIN transaction ON token.id = transaction.token_id WHERE owner.name LIKE 'John%';
SELECT DISTINCT city FROM property WHERE state IN ('California', 'Texas', 'Florida') ORDER BY city;
SELECT owner.name, wallet.balance FROM owner LEFT JOIN wallet ON owner.id = wallet.owner_id WHERE wallet.balance > 1000 ORDER BY wallet.balance DESC;
